==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Water engine
<hw>Wa"ter en"gine</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>An engine to raise water; or
an engine moved by water; also, an engine or machine for extinguishing
fires; a fire engine.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

